The last Ebola patient in the Democratic Republic of Congo has been discharged, the WHO says -- a significant step in the countdown to declaring an end to the world's 2nd-deadliest outbreak of the disease.

This is indeed wonderful news. Everyone involved in responding to this outbreak is to be congratulated. - Mod.LK]

